com.youama.nexus.parser.collector

Class CollectedItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.youama.nexus.parser.collector.CollectedItem

  • public class CollectedItem
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a collected item from a text based source code. This item can be words of a sentence or a single HTML link or a single image URL. Many instances of this item represent a full HTML page. Images, sentences, sharing links for example.
    Since:
    2015.07.11.
    Author:
    David Belicza <87.bdavid@gmail.com>
